query: Compare budget of Project Phoenix and Digital Transformation
sql:

  phoenix.total_budget AS phoenix_budget,
  digital_transformation.total_budget AS digital_transformation_budget,
  CASE 
    WHEN phoenix.total_budget > digital_transformation.total_budget THEN 'Project Phoenix has higher budget'
    WHEN phoenix.total_budget < digital_transformation.total_budget THEN 'Digital Transformation has higher budget'
    ELSE 'Both projects have the same budget'

  (SELECT total_budget FROM "projects" WHERE project_name = 'Project Phoenix') AS phoenix,

query: Show me all demands for the account 'Verizon Communications
sql:
SELECT d.* 
FROM demands d
JOIN accounts a ON d.account_id = a.account_id
WHERE a.account_name = 'Verizon Communications';
